data.description: Perfectly sited in the prized Tehaleh neighborhood behind the greenbelt. Excellent floor plan. The lower level offers two sitting areas, a fireplace, a spacious kitchen, a dining room area, and a bedroom next to a 3/4 bathroom. Stunning kitchen with walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances, and granite counters. The upper level includes a primary suite with a spa-like bath and large walk-in closet, 3 bedrooms, a laundry room, and a huge bonus room. Enjoy the large backyard and covered patio with a fireplace. 3 car garage and additional storage space. Air conditioning. Within minutes to Sprouts Holler Park and a local community cafe.
